text: Sahibzada Ishaq Zafar was an Azad Kashmiri politician. He was interim President of Azad Kashmir from 20 to 29 July 1991.http://www.ajk.gov.pk He died in 2006. == References == Category:Presidents of Azad Kashmir Category:Pakistani politicians Category:Year of birth missing Category:2006 deaths
title: Sahibzada Ishaq Zafar
